OL,3,CJim Gamble to lead independent review
OL,4,Cinto Jeffrey Donaldson's conduct
OL,6,FOn Thursday, a party statement said:
OL,7,F"The DUP has commissioned the iNEQE
OL,8,FSafeguarding Group to conduct an
OL,9,Findependent focused safeguarding
OL,10,Freview for the Democratic Unionist
OL,11,FParty into Jeffrey Donaldson's time as
OL,12,Fa member of the party.
OL,14,F"The DUP has commissioned this
OL,15,Ffocused, independent review to
OL,16,Festablish what, if any, information
OL,17,Fwas known within the party about his
OL,18,Fconduct, to examine its safeguarding
OL,19,Fand reporting arrangements, and to
OL,20,Fmake recommendations to ensure good
OL,21,Fpractice for all its members and staff.
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/5
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
