PN,41703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1783700376
OL,3,CJim Gamble to lead independent review
OL,4,Cinto Jeffrey Donaldson's conduct
OL,6,F"The review will be carried out by a
OL,7,Fspecialist multi-disciplinary team
OL,8,Ffrom the iNEQE Safeguarding Group,
OL,9,Fdrawing on their safeguarding, child
OL,10,Fprotection and policing expertise.
OL,12,F"The review will be led by Mr Jim
OL,13,FGamble.
OL,15,F"The review will be conducted entirely
OL,16,Findependent of the DUP."
OL,18,FFormer DUP leader Donaldson is in
OL,19,Fcustody awaiting sentencing following
OL,20,Fhis conviction for serious sexual
OL,21,Foffences against children.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUwD@AOUxD@XO]
