OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1783700376
OL,3,CJim Gamble to lead independent review
OL,4,Cinto Jeffrey Donaldson's conduct
OL,6,FSubsequent media reports have raised
OL,7,Fquestions about how much was known
OL,8,Fabout Donaldson's wider conduct in the
OL,9,Fperiod prior to his 2024 arrest over
OL,10,Fsex abuse allegations.
OL,12,FSome reports have contained claims
OL,13,Fthat Donaldson was allegedly engaged
OL,14,Fin behaviour in his private life that,
OL,15,Falthough legal, was at odds with
OL,16,Fpositions he adopted publicly.
OL,18,FCurrent DUP leader Gavin Robinson has
OL,19,Fpledged that the independent review he
OL,20,Fhas commissioned into Donaldson "won't
OL,21,Fleave any stone unturned".
OL,26,@|D@aOU}D@YO]
